title: Song made with Vocaloid Miriam as a lead voice
description:
The song that I created using Vocaloid Miriam software (created with the voice of Miriam Stockley) to synthesize lead vocal line. Although Vocaloid is more supposed to create back vocals, I tried it anyway and with certain success.

The vocaloid library I used is based on the voice of Miriam Stockley - the world's famous back vocalist.


you can also download it directly from
http://www.ufo-scientific.com/downloads/tpb/time_has_come(Miriam).mp3
